data.description: Welcome to this exceptional multi-family duplex located in the sought-after Sharswood section of Philadelphia – a golden opportunity for investors. With a generous 1536 square feet, this property promises comfortable urban living while catering to modern sensibilities.  Separate utility services for electricity, gas, and central heating/air conditioning ensure that both units can enjoy individualized comfort. The first unit is ingeniously designed across two levels and comprises one bedroom with another potential bedroom, office, storage or den in the lower area.  A fenced backyard, an ideal space for private entertaining and outdoor leisure, adds an attractive touch. The second unit is also split between two levels; the first level boasts two well-appointed bedrooms with good closet space and modern bathroom. The upper level boasts an open floor concept that harmonizes living spaces centered around a generously sized island – perfect for both dining and socializing. This unit expands its allure with a large deck extending from the main living area, an outdoor haven in the heart of the city.  Both units are complete with a suite of appliances, ensuring a seamless move-in experience for tenants. Premium Hardwood Floors bestow elegance throughout the property, marrying aesthetics with ease of maintenance.  Nestled along a tranquil street, the property offers a serene urban setting. A mere ten-minute drive places you in the heart of downtown Philadelphia, offering convenient access to the city's vibrant lifestyle. Local attractions, including the Philadelphia Museum, Philadelphia Zoo, and the historic Reading Terminal Market, are all within close reach. The iconic BoatHouse Row, Penn's Landing, the bustling Philadelphia Convention Center, and the Philadelphia International Airport further enrich the property's locale.  For scholars, the property is surrounded by esteemed educational institutions including Camelot Elementary, Girard College, Temple University, Drexel University, La Salle University, and the prestigious University of Pennsylvania.  With swift access to major highways such as I-76, I-95, I-476, and the PA Turnpike, commuting is hassle-free. The property also enjoys easy access to public transportation, facilitating city exploration. In addition, the short distance to the Benjamin Franklin Bridge enhances regional connectivity, linking you seamlessly to neighboring New Jersey.  Both units are presently leased on a yearly basis ensuring a steady income stream for prospective investors. The added flexibility of a 60-day notice for lease termination empowers you as the landlord, offering adaptability to evolving plans and aspirations.  In essence, this multi-family duplex blends modern comfort with investment potential, anchored in a dynamic Philadelphia neighborhood. The versatile layout, outdoor spaces, and proximity to a plethora of amenities make this property a compelling prospect for both investors and tenants. Embrace the opportunity to own a piece of this vibrant urban haven.
